 - paper title: Entropy change for the irreversible heat transfer between two finite objects
 - abstract: A positive entropy change is verified for an isolated system of two blocks of different initial temperatures and of different but finite heat capacities that are brought into contact with each other and allowed to fully thermalize.
 - publication date: 2015-07-01
 - venue: European Journal of Physics



